{"tid":2143799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"海關六度警告當局懶理 增至157死  人禍釀浩劫「誰該問吊？」","createTime":"2020-08-07T09:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T10:43:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8145825159ec8b040dc54452bfc924760938f0b","tid":2143799,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T09:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200807/W7T5OWCVPX3FJKBO3LVLQGXFHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200807%2FW7T5OWCVPX3FJKBO3LVLQGXFHY%2F&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLEt47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=8c37a5a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200807%2FW7T5OWCVPX3FJKBO3LVLQGXFHY%2F&h=ba278e4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200807/W7T5OWCVPX3FJKBO3LVLQGXFHY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n海關六度警告當局懶理 增至157死 <br />\n人禍釀浩劫「誰該問吊？」<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩貝魯特歷來最強力爆炸發生一日後，死亡人數增至157人。驚痛未平的民眾怒氣爆發，認為這場飛來橫禍是當局貪腐、疏忽、無能造成，要求官員交代。有傳媒查到文件指海關確曾就疑是今次爆炸原因的化學品示警，以及求助法庭促盡快送走，但這要求顯然未獲理會。<br />\n<br />\n貝魯特港口區於當地周二傍晚大爆炸後，總統奧恩在緊急召開的內閣會議發言，形容「貝魯特經受的恐怖是無法言傳」。他。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Eh6cuCG_edU1Dl5a-9OGH-2v1XU=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q5NFVRCLIW6RKFPOJU5JGMR24I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEh6cuCG_edU1Dl5a-9OGH-2v1XU%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ5NFVRCLIW6RKFPOJU5JGMR24I.jpg&h=dc130e8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貝魯特港口被炸毀得面目全非，近岸建築物夷為平地。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人權組織倡獨立調查<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：絕望激發怒火 誓向掌權者問責<br />\n<br />\n但國際特赦組織與人權觀察組織，均呼籲展開獨立調查，後者直言「認真憂慮黎巴嫩司法系統能否作出可信而透明的調查」。黎巴嫩少數民族德魯茲人政治人物瓊布拉特亦稱對執政者「毫不信任」，敦促獨立調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n大爆炸被認為是2 ,750公噸硝酸銨造成，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩資訊部長奈德前日確認，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當局矢言徹查事件，但民眾早認定。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ArRu_zA2I-VSOy-6AwKZ9iIb7tg=/993x609/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZXM7VZN4NDBSUKM7KLGAUHOCBU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FArRu_zA2I-VSOy-6AwKZ9iIb7tg%3D%2F993x609%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZXM7VZN4NDBSUKM7KLGAUHOCBU.gif&h=640a9767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n空中巴士國防航天公司公開貝魯特港口發生爆炸前後的衞星照片。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無清理瓦礫 被轟垃圾政府<br />\n<br />\n爆炸後街上瓦礫雜物垃圾散佈，未見官方清理。在貝魯特著名酒吧區，數百人自發在打掃。42歲的法德拉拉極勞氣：「這個政府就。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/法新社"},{"pid":"36e1b675955b5c2ba24879e37b700d04fcab8501","tid":2143799,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"個窿嘅左手邊重有棟建築物未冧，嗰棟咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec5592aecbbe839f022c6c58ae908e7de5dd0bc","tid":2143799,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36e1b675955b5c2ba24879e37b700d04fcab8501","tid":2143799,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"個窿嘅左手邊重有棟建築物未冧，嗰棟咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"糧倉好似係"},{"pid":"1c1d4ce953c8821c6005a523991cb634d12fdcb5","tid":2143799,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec5592aecbbe839f022c6c58ae908e7de5dd0bc","tid":2143799,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36e1b675955b5c2ba24879e37b700d04fcab8501","tid":2143799,"uid":156618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:38:27.000Z","msg":"個窿嘅左手邊重有棟建築物未冧，嗰棟咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"糧倉好似係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07